Well here it is!

After a long development and beta testing period we can finally present the most anticipated CSS map to the fpsbanana community.

Widely played on almost every PL server and LAN tournament. With controversial name and design this map stormed polish css community like a blizzard.
Created using Feng Shui principles and concepts it provides tons of fun.

Find out for yourself!
